sentences: Greg Thompson is an American record executive currently serving as President of Maverick (company).
Previously, Thompson worked at Island Def Jam, Elektra Records, and Chrysalis Records.
Thompson currently resides in Los Angeles, CA with his family.

sentences: Thompson was recruited to EMI Records in February 2008.
At the end of 2012, Universal Music Group purchased EMI Music.

In 2013, Thompson became the EVP of the newly reinvented Capitol Music Group, continuing to work with and develop artists such as Katy Perry, Bastille, Beck, Jennifer Lopez, Sam Smith and many more from Hollywood, CA.

On April 6, 2016 it was announced that Thompson would be departing his position at Capitol to become President of Maverick Music, a conglomeration of some of the most powerful management companies in the world.
His last day at Capitol was June 1.
